cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.HC 

This paper belongs to the software engineering subfield of computer science, as it focuses on analyzing user reviews of mobile apps to gain insights for software engineers. Therefore, cs.SE is the most likely sub-category. 

The paper also involves data mining and analysis, which could fall under cs.CY (computational methods) and cs.IR (information retrieval). 

The study also touches on user experience and sentiment analysis, which could be categorized under cs.SI (social and information networks) and cs.HC (human-computer interaction).
